FBIS3-29948 "dreas037_c_94033" FBIS-EAS-94-037 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Feb 1994 North Korea Events Mark 30th Anniversary of Rural Theses Symposium Held in Pyongyang SK2302045894 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0443 GMT 23 Feb 94 SK2302045894 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, February 23 (KCNA) -- A national symposium was held here Tuesday marking the 30th anniversary of the publication of "Theses on the Socialist Rural Question in Our Country", a work of the great leader President Kim Il-song (February 25, 1964). The rural theses is a flawless great programme of socialist rural construction which gives comprehensive and perfect answers to all the theoretical and practical questions arising in the solution of the rural questions ranging from the essence of the socialist rural question and the basic principle of its solution to the tasks for the building of the socialist countryside and ways for their fulfilment. The symposium was attended by Yi Chong-ok, Politburo member of the C.C. [Central Committee], the Workers' Party of Korea and vice-president; Hong Song- nam, alternate Politburo member of the C.C., the WPK and vice-premier of the Administration Council; Kim Ki-nam and So Kwan-hui, secretaries of the C.C., the WPK, and other officials concerned. Speakers stressed that the respected leader Comrade Kim Il-song, on the basis of the chuche idea, set forth the programme of rural construction that indicates scientifically and theoretically the way of resolving the peasant and agricultural problems in conformity with the essential requirements of socialist society, thereby spreading the first bright blueprint in history for a final solution of the rural question and providing a powerful ideological and theoretical weapon for vigorously pushing on socialist rural construction. They said the theses on the socialist rural question is an immortal great programme of socialist rural construction whose truth and validity have been verified through practice. They noted that it is world-historic feats performed by the great leader Comrade Kim Il-song and the dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il in accomplishing the cause of socialism that our country has been effecting fundamental changes in rural construction and successfully resolving the peasant and agricultural problems by implementing the socialist rural theses with success. The speakers laid stress on the need to study and grasp more deeply our party's idea and theory on socialist rural construction and continuously consolidate and develop the achievements made in implementing the rural theses, thus defending and glorifying Korean-style socialism.
